data.description: Diamond Floor plan by Trophy Signature homes built in 2021 in Parkside Village.This Modern home features an open concept layout with a large living room and a spacious kitchen.The Kitchen offers white quartz, white backsplash, white cabinets, and stainless steel appliances with plenty of storage space. Living room offers a cozy electric fireplace with plenty of open space for gatherings and entertainment. Light flooring and light colors through out the house. Sellers will consider leaving washer and dryer, and fridge with strong offer.
